    • bind

      public void bind(IuResource<T> resource)
      Description copied from interface: IuResourceReference
      Binds a resource to all referrer instances.

      A reference to the bound resource will be provided to all referrer instances accepted prior to binding. Once bound, new referrer instances will be provided a reference to the resource when accepted.

      Specified by:
      bind in interface IuResourceReference<R,T>
      Parameters:
